{"translationLines":[{"lineNumber":108491,"originalJapaneseLine":"「男性とは……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Men are...\""},{"lineNumber":108492,"originalJapaneseLine":"「時にあれほど情熱的に……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"At times, so passionate...\""},{"lineNumber":108493,"originalJapaneseLine":"　己の心をさらけ出せるものなんですね」","translatedEnglishLine":"They can bare their hearts like that.\""},{"lineNumber":108494,"originalJapaneseLine":"「私の人生では……考えられないことです」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"In my life... it's something I cannot imagine.\""},{"lineNumber":108495,"originalJapaneseLine":"（男性とデートなんて初めてでしたが……","translatedEnglishLine":"(It was my first time dating a man...)"},{"lineNumber":108496,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あんな風になるものなのですね）","translatedEnglishLine":"I didn’t know it would be like that.)"},{"lineNumber":108497,"originalJapaneseLine":"サクラは、熱く掴まれた肩を、","translatedEnglishLine":"Sakura gently touched the shoulder that was clasped tightly and warmly."},{"lineNumber":108498,"originalJapaneseLine":"無意識にそっと触れていた。","translatedEnglishLine":"She touched it softly, unconsciously."},{"lineNumber":108499,"originalJapaneseLine":"（今日のことは良き思い出としてこのまま……）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Let today remain as a good memory like this…)"},{"lineNumber":108500,"originalJapaneseLine":"常に固い表情を浮かべるサクラのそれが、","translatedEnglishLine":"Sakura, who always wore a stern expression,"},{"lineNumber":108501,"originalJapaneseLine":"今だけは少しだけ朗らかだった。","translatedEnglishLine":"was just a little cheerful—only this once."},{"lineNumber":108502,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いや、待て……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"No, wait...\""},{"lineNumber":108503,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あれは一般的な男性像からはかけ離れておるぞ」","translatedEnglishLine":"That is far from the typical image of a man.\""},{"lineNumber":108504,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……ッ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...!\""},{"lineNumber":108505,"originalJapaneseLine":"「むむ、こ、これは……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm, th-this is...\""},{"lineNumber":108506,"originalJapaneseLine":"「たまたまパステルの部屋に遊びに来たら、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I just happened to come visit Pastel’s room,"},{"lineNumber":108507,"originalJapaneseLine":"　運が良かったような……驚いたような……」","translatedEnglishLine":"and it was like luck... and surprise... at the same time.\""},{"lineNumber":108508,"originalJapaneseLine":"「っ、あ、申し訳ありません。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, I’m sorry."},{"lineNumber":108509,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ただ今、着替え中ですので……」","translatedEnglishLine":"I'm just changing clothes right now...\""},

{"lineNumber":108510,"originalJapaneseLine":"「えーと……一応確認だ……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Um... just to confirm...\""},{"lineNumber":108511,"originalJapaneseLine":"　お前は……","translatedEnglishLine":"You are...?"},{"lineNumber":108512,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……サクラ・カラーです」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Sakura Kala.\""},{"lineNumber":108513,"originalJapaneseLine":"「だな……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"That’s right...\""},{"lineNumber":108514,"originalJapaneseLine":"「しかし……うぅむ、これは中々……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"However... hmm, this is quite something...\""},{"lineNumber":108515,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……っ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...!\""},{"lineNumber":108516,"originalJapaneseLine":"サクラは居心地が悪そうに肌を隠した。","translatedEnglishLine":"Sakura hid her skin awkwardly, looking uncomfortable."},{"lineNumber":108517,"originalJapaneseLine":"「しかし何故、いつもは顔を隠す」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"But why do you always hide your face?\""},{"lineNumber":108518,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……私は影ですから」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Because I am a shadow.\""},{"lineNumber":108519,"originalJapaneseLine":"「可愛いのにもったいない。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It’s a waste, since you’re cute."},{"lineNumber":108520,"originalJapaneseLine":"　そんなんじゃいい男が寄ってこないぞ」","translatedEnglishLine":"At that rate, no good man will come near you.\""},{"lineNumber":108521,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そう、俺様のようなな」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Like me, for example.\""},{"lineNumber":108522,"originalJapaneseLine":"「恋愛に興味はありませんので」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I’m not interested in romance.\""},{"lineNumber":108523,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""},{"lineNumber":108524,"originalJapaneseLine":"「こらこら、服を着るんじゃない。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hey, hey, don’t put on clothes."},{"lineNumber":108525,"originalJapaneseLine":"　もっと俺を楽しませて――」","translatedEnglishLine":"Entertain me more—\""},{"lineNumber":108526,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いえ、もう時間切れです」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"No, time’s up already.\""},{"lineNumber":108527,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なに？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What?\""},{"lineNumber":108528,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あ、おとーさんだー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, Daddy’s here!\""},{"lineNumber":108529,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ぐおっ、リセット！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Gah! Reset!?\""},{"lineNumber":108530,"originalJapaneseLine":"部屋に帰ってきたリセットが","translatedEnglishLine":"Reset, who returned to the room,"},{"lineNumber":108531,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランスに気づいて足に飛びついてきた。","translatedEnglishLine":"noticed Rance and jumped onto his leg."},

{"lineNumber":108532,"originalJapaneseLine":"「えへへへー、どーしたの？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hehehe, what's wrong?\""},{"lineNumber":108533,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いや、これはその……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Well, this is... um...\""},{"lineNumber":108534,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あっ、もうサクラがいない」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, Sakura’s already gone.\""},{"lineNumber":108535,"originalJapaneseLine":"「くう、逃げられた……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ugh, she escaped...\""},{"lineNumber":108536,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ねーねー、遊ぼー」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hey, hey, let’s play!\""},{"lineNumber":108537,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""},{"lineNumber":108538,"originalJapaneseLine":"「折り紙でもするか……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Shall we do some origami...?\""},{"lineNumber":108539,"originalJapaneseLine":"「わーい！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yay!\""},{"lineNumber":108540,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""},{"lineNumber":108541,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……ふう」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Phew.\""},{"lineNumber":108542,"originalJapaneseLine":"「恋人として、出来るだけのことをしよう」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"As a lover, I will do everything I can.\""},{"lineNumber":108543,"originalJapaneseLine":"イージスがランス城の中を散歩していた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Aegis was taking a walk inside Rance Castle."},{"lineNumber":108544,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あ、おい、見ろよ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, hey, look...\""},{"lineNumber":108545,"originalJapaneseLine":"「イージスさんか……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Is that Aegis...?"},{"lineNumber":108546,"originalJapaneseLine":"　うぅむ、今日も美しい……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Hmm, so beautiful again today...\""},{"lineNumber":108547,"originalJapaneseLine":"「長く青い髪がサラサラと舞って、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Her long blue hair flows gently,"},{"lineNumber":108548,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ただ歩くだけでなんと絵になる人か……」","translatedEnglishLine":"just walking, she looks like a painting...\""},{"lineNumber":108549,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ん？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hm?\""},{"lineNumber":108550,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""}]}

